erages and multiple packaged goods.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h3>Solution&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n<p>A major area of confusion was preparing for beverage dispensation and collecting dispensed items&nbsp;especially when multiple items are purchased. Dispensation failures need to be handled immediately. For this reason, I paid special attention to our UX in this area. I designed around anticipated user behavior pitfalls without causing annoyance. Multiple other improvements enable upsell of products, brand engagement and support point in time promotions.<\\/p>\\n<p><img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000035.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vend img3\\\" width=\\\"1102\\\" height=\\\"801\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n<p>The design makes it easy to instantly scan and connect to any machine. Furthermore, for frequently used machines, one-touch access provides an instant connection. To work around difficulties in scanning QR codes, a fallback option allows for easy entering of a PIN.<\\/p>\\n<p><img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000034.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vend img1\\\" width=\\\"1168\\\" height=\\\"791\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"font-family: verdana, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.2px;\\\">The design of the selection page provided a way to showcase branded products with large images. The selection is easy with just a simple plus (+) button. The major innovation is that selected items drop into a cart on the same screen resulting in instant confirmation and increased confidence in the selection.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<div class=\\\"gmail-wpb_wrapper\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\n<p><img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000033.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vend img 2\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"863\\\" \\/><\\/p>\",\"banner_image\":\"40\",\"thumbnail\":\"39\"}','{\"details\":\"<h3>Brief<\\/h3>\\n<p>Vendekin is disrupting the vending machine ecosystem. They&rsquo;re introducing cashless payments, product upselling, operator efficiency,&nbsp;and brand engagement.<\\/p>\\n<p>I engaged with Vendekin to apply design thinking and craft a delightful user experience for the modern, consumer-facing vending app. Make the app fun, intuitive, and highly efficient thereby allowing people on-the-go to quickly and predictably complete their vending transactions.<\\/p>\\n<h3>Approach<\\/h3>\\n<p>The design focused on addressing three main areas of user confusion.<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Connect the app&nbsp;to a particular machine within seconds or sooner.<\\/li>\\n<li>Make the selection process clear and fun.<\\/li>\\n<li>Design around the confusion when dispensing beverages and multiple packaged goods.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h3>Solution&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n<p>A major area of confusion was preparing for beverage dispensation and collecting dispensed items&nbsp;especially when multiple items are purchased. Dispensation failures need to be handled immediately. For this reason, I paid special attention to our UX in this area. I designed around anticipated user behavior pitfalls without causing annoyance. Multiple other improvements enable upsell of products, brand engagement and support point in time promotions.<\\/p>\\n<p><img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000035.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vend img3\\\" width=\\\"1102\\\" height=\\\"801\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n<p>The design makes it easy to instantly scan and connect to any machine. Furthermore, for frequently used machines, one-touch access provides an instant connection. To work around difficulties in scanning QR codes, a fallback option allows for easy entering of a PIN.<\\/p>\\n<p><img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000034.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vend img1\\\" width=\\\"1168\\\" height=\\\"791\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"font-family: verdana, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.2px;\\\">The design of the selection page provided a way to showcase branded products with large images. The selection is easy with just a simple plus (+) button. The major innovation is that selected items drop into a cart on the same screen resulting in instant confirmation and increased confidence in the selection.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<div class=\\\"gmail-wpb_wrapper\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\n<p><img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000033.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vend img 2\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"863\\\" \\/><\\/p>\",\"id\":\"18\"}',NULL,NULL,1,'2019-06-12 16:17:17','192.168.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_14_5) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/74.0.3729.169 Safari/537.36'),(515,'ENTRY','UPDATE','27','projects',27,1,'{\"id\":\"27\",\"status\":\"1\",\"sort\":null,\"project_type_id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Nap26\",\"subtitle\":\"Sleep, Recharge, Rejuvenate\",\"details\":\"<h2>NAP26<\\/h2>\\n<p>This audio program uses pulsating beats to create sound vibration which match natural sleeping patterns, signaling the brain to enter a more relaxed state. NAP26 wakes you after 26 minutes, researched as the optimum length of time for a powernap.<\\/p>\\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000078.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Nap 26\\\" width=\\\"1280\\\" height=\\\"583\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"banner_image\":null,\"thumbnail\":\"79\"}','{\"details\":\"<h2>NAP26<\\/h2>\\n<p>This audio program uses pulsating beats to create sound vibration which match natural sleeping patterns, signaling the brain to enter a more relaxed state. NAP26 wakes you after 26 minutes, researched as the optimum length of time for a powernap.<\\/p>\\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\\\"\\/storage\\/uploads\\/00000000078.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Nap 26\\\" width=\\\"1280\\\" height=\\\"583\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"id\":\"27\"}',NULL,NULL,1,'2019-06-12 16:19:14','192.168.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_14_5) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/74.0.3729.169 Safari/537.36'),(516,'FILES','ADD','1','directus_files',156,1,'{\"id\":\"156\",\"status\":\"1\",\"name\":\"00000000156.png\",\"title\":\"Screen Shot 2019 06 12 at 9.50.48 PM\",\"location\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"type\":\"image\\/png\",\"charset\":\"binary\",\"tags\":\"\",\"width\":\"1428\",\"height\":\"648\",\"size\":\"